{"tid":1081318,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃大仙虐鴿狂徒公然樹技殺鴿　熱心市民目擊報警","createTime":"2019-03-28T08:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T09:11:03.000Z","uid":1886,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"981cacd6fdc9060edf18fe770d2f2097bc92abb8","tid":1081318,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:20:42.000Z","msg":"黃大仙鳳德邨虐鴿狂徒今日中午公然以樹枝打死白鴿，想放入環保袋中帶走，熱心市民李小姐當場喝止及報警，那狂徒急忙將白鴿丟下逃走。警方接報後拘捕一名69歲姓蔡男子，涉嫌殘酷對待動物，案件交黃大仙警區刑事調查隊第二隊跟進。李小姐對本報表示，之前因為聽到鳳德邨有人虐鴿，所以今日特別過來看看，希望能夠防止虐鴿事件再發生，想不到目擊案件。<br />\n<br />\n李小姐表示，今日中午約1時45分，她見到有一名男子在引水道山坡那邊，以樹枝打死一隻白鴿，然後拾起白鴿想放入環保袋中，白鴿口部滴出鮮血。<br />\n<br />\n她說：「我即刻喝止他，問他做什麼事，他反說不關我事，我說要報警，他就丟掉那白鴿走了。」她說當時還有兩名途人目擊事件。李小姐報警後，到場警員認為事態嚴重，找來重案組跟進，她則到警署落口供。<br />\n<br />\n鳳德邨上周四亦發生兩隻白鴿分別被繩纏頸及腳，倒臥於引水道位置，最終死亡，懷疑涉及人為虐待。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.hkanimalpost.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/%E6%AE%BA%E9%B4%BF%E7%8B%82%E5%BE%92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkanimalpost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E9%25B4%25BF%25E7%258B%2582%25E5%25BE%2592.jpg&h=c96bcc08&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkanimalpost.com/2019/03/27/03273/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkanimalpost.com%2F2019%2F03%2F27%2F03273%2F&d=pW%2BpET2SRZmQ0hv433X7AEqdoMPUcUEfVTbHbk%2Bo2EU%3D&h=acd24615\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkanimalpost.com/2019/03/27/03273/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">殺得好！幾時過嚟中環幫幫手</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76f8e506dc623a80cafa56f8c7f31151b4d1f8a","tid":1081318,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:24:56.000Z","msg":"【鴿子殺手】野鴿繩纏頸腳奄奄一息　 樹枝攻擊鴿子　怪漢被捕<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/310938/鴿子殺手-野鴿繩纏頸腳奄奄一息-樹枝攻擊鴿子-怪漢被捕\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F310938%2F%E9%B4%BF%E5%AD%90%E6%AE%BA%E6%89%8B-%E9%87%8E%E9%B4%BF%E7%B9%A9%E7%BA%8F%E9%A0%B8%E8%85%B3%E5%A5%84%E5%A5%84%E4%B8%80%E6%81%AF-%E6%A8%B9%E6%9E%9D%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A%E9%B4%BF%E5%AD%90-%E6%80%AA%E6%BC%A2%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95&d=pW%2BpET2SRZmQ0hv433X7AEqdoMPUcUEfVTbHbk%2Bo2EU%3D&h=402c58f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/310938/鴿子殺手-野鴿繩纏頸腳奄奄一息-樹枝攻擊鴿子-怪漢被捕</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2604528/org/c343ecfe2325755d3cbf0161f0a6e914.jpg/EL0E074rX_uU1NI7JHqvWp3l0EH2oReKvqzCab6swmk?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2604528%2Forg%2Fc343ecfe2325755d3cbf0161f0a6e914.jpg%2FEL0E074rX_uU1NI7JHqvWp3l0EH2oReKvqzCab6swmk%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=f28575b1&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n東九龍發生虐鴿事件！昨午（27日）約二時許，有街坊目賭一名男子以樹枝攻擊鴿子，遂報警求助。經初步調查，警方傍晚於鳳德邨斑鳳樓一單位，拘捕一名69歲姓蔡男子，懷疑他以樹枝拍打一隻白鴿導致白鴿死亡。他涉殘酷對待動物被捕，案件交由黃大仙警區刑事調查隊第二隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2603930/org/fa0f69fecf09fb113d546ad15e0d9979.jpg/m_qMwG1ME9ykMew16ALFg9zzsrcF57clCMXPJAjFzyQ?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2603930%2Forg%2Ffa0f69fecf09fb113d546ad15e0d9979.jpg%2Fm_qMwG1ME9ykMew16ALFg9zzsrcF57clCMXPJAjFzyQ%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=b55d82a9&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n上周四（21日）鳳德邨，兩隻分別頸及腳被繩纏繞的鴿子，倒臥於引水道位置，及後由餵貓義工發現後向愛協救助，惟兩鴿先後死亡。有居民指，上址後山位置曾有可疑男子以「老鼠膠」捉鴿，膠版上遺下大量鴿毛，惟未知是否與今次的虐鴿事件有關。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2604444/org/4169f9ee3196ac2a7b0fa150831bdf72.jpg/JH8pNb21ozS6gcW4TuQHZFAbscCS7P49Kl2mPQNdpj0?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2604444%2Forg%2F4169f9ee3196ac2a7b0fa150831bdf72.jpg%2FJH8pNb21ozS6gcW4TuQHZFAbscCS7P49Kl2mPQNdpj0%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=1c00b14d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">懷疑涉案男子，手握鴿子。</span></div>"},{"pid":"7dd0dc87242e95fcafb0ab8cd648f902e9f6ed61","tid":1081318,"uid":34368,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:27:56.000Z","msg":"大陸仔"},{"pid":"0d88a850c00052ec994fb40c75a8d9dfa26f409e","tid":1081318,"uid":52605,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:30:40.000Z","msg":"殺咗再帶走<br />\n似係大陸佬捉鴿食"},{"pid":"781543f5019c335d4681d1ab52c54320a292db15","tid":1081318,"uid":11258,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:30:54.000Z","msg":"廢老得閒無野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9bd5b5a475953cc889fca147495c9a57eb8f356","tid":1081318,"uid":95637,"like":5,"dislike":11,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:38:42.000Z","msg":"殺曬佢啦<br />\n鴿見到都覺得核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74b176276798bfd0228ad3f2efac48c1eb51f70","tid":1081318,"uid":104658,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:41:38.000Z","msg":"替天行道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf3138cd475d0fbe1612c3e6e8fa3e6c8f221ed","tid":1081318,"uid":103013,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:43:06.000Z","msg":"草木竹石皆可為劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ca1e62e14c050c40cc8b17bfcc6ad0a457ec94a","tid":1081318,"uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T08:46:25.000Z","msg":"中環多鴿到出馬路，間唔中仲會俾車碌扁爆頭，啲腸咇哂出嚟再俾之後啲車碌下碌下搞到成條街都係，勁唔衛生但係好似從來都無機構正視過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"318784e322271152ec4d73caca691a08d32cbf1a","tid":1081318,"uid":130695,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7dd0dc87242e95fcafb0ab8cd648f902e9f6ed61"